t;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/25/24082760/apple-smart-glasses-airpods-cameras-smart-ring&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;美国诉苹果：你需要知道的一切&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24107581/doj-v-apple-antitrust-monoply-news-updates&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;E6INSh&quot;>;在这里，我们精选了各型号目前最优惠的价格，包括入门级 AirPods、AirPods Pro、第三代 AirPods 和 AirPods Max。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;Hh97yA&quot;>; &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://s3.amazonaws.com/assets.sbnation.com/csk/uploads/verge-toc.css&quot;>; &lt; div class=&quot;duet--article--article-body-component verge-table-of-contents border-franklin border&quot; id=&quot;toc-main&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;ej2msf&quot; >;最佳 AirPods（第二代）优惠&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;upOxaE&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:9502973&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;layout&quot;:&quot; full_with_square_img&quot;}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;eg29V6&quot;>;2021 年，Apple 降低了第二代 AirPods 的定价 - 现在是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T11:11:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T11:11:54-04:00</updated><title>如何将您的主题帖子交叉发布到 fediverse</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量拼贴画显示使用线程的各个方面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Unbld2im6lM8P35CAiQin3fjBwI=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246878/HT055_THREADS_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;KeBFdu&quot;>;看起来联邦宇宙正在开放。 3 月底，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107881/threads-fediverse-beta-launch-mastodon&quot;>;Meta 的 Threads 推出了一项测试版功能&lt;/a>;，该功能允许来自美国、加拿大或日本的用户可以交叉发布并查看 Mastodon 以及其他联合社交网络的点赞。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;rhvH3V&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Threads 的 fediverse 测试版开放，分享您在 Mastodon 上的帖子，太&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107881/threads-fediverse-beta-launch-mastodon&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;JdCY4Y&quot;>;如果您是来自这三个国家之一的 Threads 用户，并且想尝试一下此测试版，那么这并不困难。您可以通过移动应用程序或网络版本执行此操作：&lt;/p>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;JYi24z&quot;>;在 Threads 的移动应用程序中，点击右下角的&lt;strong>;个人资料图标&lt;/strong>; ，点击右上角的两行，然后选择&lt;strong>;帐户>; Fediverse 分享&lt;/strong>;。&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;eGAtUd&quot;>;在网页版上，点击右上角的两行，然后选择&lt;strong>;设置 >;帐户选项卡 >; Fediverse 共享&lt;/strong>;。&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;在...中查找 Fediverse 共享选项&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt; /figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T10:15:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T10:15:00-04:00</updated><title> Mailchimp 首席执行官 Rania Succar 解释了为什么电子邮件公司对 Intuit 有意义</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Intuit Mailchimp 首席执行官 Rania Succar 的肖像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5Z7AFg4I31q9jlJ23BsC-y-LKY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn。 vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246692/VRG_DCD_Rania_Succar.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图：The Verge / Intuit Mailchimp 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Intuit 购买了 Mailchimp 2021 年，不到一年后，联合创始人本·切斯特纳特 (Ben Chestnut) 离职。以下是新任首席执行官 Rania Succar 的发展历程。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24115515/intuit-mailchimp-ceo-rania-succar-acquisition-email-marketing- ai-small-business-decoder-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24115515/intuit-mailchimp-ceo-rania-succar-acquisition-email-marketing-ai-small-business-decoder-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24115515/intuit-mailchimp-ceo-rania-succar-acquisition-email-marketing-ai-small-business-decoder-interview</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T10:02:38-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T10:02:38-04:00</updated><title>最适合训练和日常生活的 Garmin 手表</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;彩色背景上的几款 Garmin 手表&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5dtgeyIVuFtgCeI1hMNSF_9Epo=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72245384/236645_Buying_Guide_Garmin_Watches_WJoel.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Garmins 不再只是多项运动的庞然大物。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Will Joel / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Garmin 可能以其硬核健身手表而闻名，但它也提供广泛的生活方式产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T09:44:32-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T09:44:32-04:00</updated><title>随着反垄断压力的加大，微软将 Teams 从 Office 中剥离出来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Microsoft Teams 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pUw5jRH3mqylqJy4PYpd9RzBD-g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246598/STK264_MICROSOFT_TEAMS_V2_CVIRGINIA _B.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;j3bPZN&quot;>;微软可能希望转移欧盟正在进行的反垄断调查的打击，正在将 Teams 从 Office 365 剥离到作为自己的独立应用程序在全球销售，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-separate-teams-office-globally-amid-antitrust-scrutiny-2024-04-01/&quot;>;&lt; em>;路透社今天报道&lt;/a>;。公司发言人 Robin Koch 通过电子邮件告诉 The Verge，微软正在对其商务聊天和会议应用程序进行更改，“以确保客户的清晰度”。 .com/eupolicy/2023/08/31/european-competition-teams-office-microsoft-365/&quot;>;去年欧盟就已经这样做了&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;m61hXU&quot;>;根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;amp;mid=24542&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https% 3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Flicensing%2Fnews%2FMicrosoft365-Teams-WW&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;新的 Microsoft 博客文章&lt;/a>;，宣布在全球推出由于欧盟的变化，微软的现有客户应该能够保留他们当前的交易，该交易将 Teams 与 Office 和其他产品捆绑在一起，续订、更新或选择新的产品。对于任何新注册的人来说，Teams 本身的费用为 5.25 美元...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft- team-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft-teams-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft-teams-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T08:05:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T08:05:03-04:00</updated><title> Gmail 20 周年</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人皱着眉头被电子邮件包围的像素插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/G9FI3Ogh4Go2dRmOuwTM5V7wfE8=/0x0:1750x1167/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73241540/247048_Gmail_20_Years_1750_NLi ttle.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Nick Little 为 